Bug ID:013
Title: 13.Uploading a file is not required but cannot continue without one.
Description: You cannot make a reservation without uploading a file.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on Locations in the navbar.
Step 4 : Select your location.
Step 5 : Select a month.
Step 6 : Reserve a date.
Step 7 : Click the Reserve button.


Expected Result:
When Reserving a location you are required to fill in Your Name and Email, but you are not required to add a file that describes the purpose of your reservation.
Actual Result:
You cannot make a reservation without adding a file that describes the purpose of your reservation.

Severity:
High  

Priority:
High

Additional Information:
-

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
